column6: Graphic novel set in an alternate reality where superheroes changed the course of history.
A dystopian tale about a vigilante fighting against tyranny.
The retelling of Batman's origins and early days as a vigilante.
The adventures of Goku and his quest to collect the seven Dragon Balls.
A love letter to Peter Parker's past and his memories of Gwen Stacy.
The first volume of the cyberpunk manga that inspired a generation.
The journey of a young ninja striving to become the strongest in his village.
A supernatural thriller about a notebook that can kill anyone whose name is written in it.
Two brothers try to restore their bodies using alchemy after a failed experiment.
Luffy sets off on his adventure to become the King of the Pirates.
A dark look into the Joker's origin story and his confrontation with Batman.
Tanjiro's journey to save his sister and avenge his family from demons.
Two orphans dream of becoming the Wizard King in a world of magic.
The story of survival in a world overrun by zombies.
A young man transforms into a half-ghoul after an attack and must learn to navigate his new life.
A teenager accidentally gains the powers of a Soul Reaper and must take on the duties of one.
A young boy born without superpowers in a world of heroes strives to become the greatest hero.
Jonathan Joestar's battle against the evil vampire Dio.
